h-icon\" href=\"/logo.png\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/polyfills-42372ed130431b0a.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"antialiased\"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><div class=\"min-h-screen flex bg-grid-green\" style=\"background:var(--bg-main)\"><div class=\"hidden lg:flex flex-col justify-between w-[420px] shrink-0 p-10\" style=\"border-right:1px solid var(--table-border)\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\"><img src=\"/logo.png\" alt=\"Logo\" class=\"w-8 h-8 object-contain\"/></div><div><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold mb-2\" style=\"color:var(--text-primary)\">Commencez gratuitement dès aujourd&#x27;hui</h2><p class=\"text-[13px] text-[#5a7a5a] mb-6\">Tout ce dont vous avez besoin pour construire une automatisation WhatsApp puissante.</p><ul class=\"space-y-3\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check text-[#22c55e] shrink-0\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-[13px] text-[#8a9a8a]\">Essai gratuit de 7 jours (plan Basic)</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check text-[#22c55e] shrink-0\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-[13px] text-[#8a9a8a]\">Jusqu&#x27;à 1 instance WhatsApp gratuite</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check text-[#22c55e] shrink-0\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-[13px] text-[#8a9a8a]\">Accès API avec webhooks</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check text-[#22c55e] shrink-0\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-[13px] text-[#8a9a8a]\">Suivi des messages en temps réel</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check text-[#22c55e] shrink-0\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-[13px] text-[#8a9a8a]\">Évoluez à tout moment vers plus d&#x27;instances</span></li></ul></div><div class=\"p-4 rounded-xl\" style=\"background:var(--green-bg-subtle);border:1px solid var(--green-border-subtle)\"><p class=\"text-[12px] text-[#22c55e] font-semibold mb-1\">Le plan gratuit inclut</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-[#5a7a5a]\">Essai gratuit 7 jours · 1 instance · Accès complet à l&#x27;API</p></div></div><div class=\"flex-1 flex flex-col p-6\"><div class=\"w-full max-w-2xl mx-auto flex flex-col h-full\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px)\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-6\"><img src=\"/logo.png\" alt=\"Logo\" class=\"w-8 h-8 object-contain\"/><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-500 text-white text-sm font-semibold px-5 py-2 rounded-lg transition-colors\" href=\"/login\">Se connecter</a></div><div class=\"mb-6\